        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This function returns the interrupt mask to know which interrupts are enabled and which of them were disabled. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to <ref refid="struct_x_csu_dma" kindref="compound">XCsuDma</ref> instance to be worked on. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Channel</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
